Ramkumar

Ramkumar is a Kannada Actor known for the movies Mutthina Haara(1990), Habba(1999), Swalpa Adjust Madkolli(2000)

Place Of BirthBangalore, KarnatakaWiki Pagehttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramkumar FatherShringar Nagaraj Biography

Ramkumar is Indian film actor and producer working in Kannada language films who made his debut in Peraala's 1990 action film Aavesha (2012)
